<App layout="vertical">
  <AppHeader>
    <Text fontWeight="bold">xmlui-desktop</Text>
    <Theme paddingHorizontal-Button-sm="$space-1">
      <HStack gap="$space-0_5">
        <Button
          label="A−"
          variant="ghost"
          tooltip="Decrease app font size"
          onClick="window.setAppFontSize(window.getAppFontSize() - 1)" />
        <Button
          label="A+"
          variant="ghost"
          tooltip="Increase app font size"
          onClick="window.setAppFontSize(window.getAppFontSize() + 1)" />
      </HStack>
    </Theme>
  </AppHeader>

  <VStack padding="$space-6" gap="$space-4" maxWidth="640px">
    <Markdown content="# Welcome

This is the xmlui-desktop project. Unless you are developing this
project, you probably want to launch `xmlui-desktop` in a directory
that contains your own XMLUI project. Then use the top-toolbar
`agent tools` button to open the drawer with five views:

- **Talk** — live transcript of the current agent session (alternating
  user / assistant turns, spinner while waiting). The drawer's pinned
  AppHeader has 🎤 voice — click from any tab to dictate.
- **Worklist** — pending items the agent has proposed
  (`resources/proposal.json`); approve or drop with one click.
- **Commits** — recent commits with one-click push.
- **Sessions** — read/search past Claude and Codex transcripts.
- **README** — this project's README for quick reference." />
  </VStack>
</App>
